data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET AT NO FAULT TO THE SELLER. Discover your own personal haven on North Haven Lane! Nestled in the charming town of Perry, GA, this 4-sided brick residence graces a serene neighborhood just moments from I-75, local schools, and downtown Perry. Enjoy 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms arranged in a thoughtfully split floorplan.  Step into the living area, adorned with a coffered ceiling for an air of sophistication. The adjacent eat-in kitchen beckons with a breakfast bar, pantry, and plentiful cabinetry, creating a functional and inviting space. The Owner's Suite offers a private retreat with a bathroom featuring a double vanity, soaking tub, water closet, and a stylish tile shower.  Beyond the walls, the expansive privacy-fenced backyard on this .67-acre lot provides ample room for relaxation and recreation. Embrace the lifestyle this residence affords—call today to arrange a tour and envision your next chapter!
